sName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname type=\"patronym\">\u003Cseg type=\"I\">Ματρ\u003C/seg>\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" quantity=\"3\" unit=\"character\"/>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname type=\"idionym\">\u003Cgap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/>\u003Cseg part=\"F\">ιας\u003C/seg>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text after Arena.\u003C/note>\u003C!-- ISicDef no. 1 -->\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n                \u003Cp/>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\">\n                \u003Cp/>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n                \u003Cp>4-5. Incised upside down and probably added later; ΡΙΣΤΟ, tablet; Ἀριστο̄́ι (not identical to A. of L. 1, whose descent is not specified) plus patronymic (either Μάτρ[ο̄] from Μᾶτρος or Μάτρ[ιος] from Μᾶτρις) or matronymic (Ματρ[οῦς] from Ματρο̄́ι). (SEG)\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>38.0935\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Cordano\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1988\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>14 no. 2\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F8BUYFFR\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002411\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002411\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                        \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IGASM2[2]\">\n                            \u003Cauthor>Arena\u003C/author>\n                            \u003Cdate>2002\u003C/date>\n                            \u003CcitedRange>132\u003C/citedRange>\n                            \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/65P7AM6N\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001373\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001373\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
